info.name: TacTix
info.attribution: Game design and layout by LawDawg96.  Released to the Public Domain under CC0.
info.description: Do not be the last person to remove a tile from the board in this classic strategy game.
info.ruleText:
Select the format: 4x4 square, 6x6 square, or 5x5 hexagon.

Players take turns clicking on one or more adjacent pieces from a row or column. The player that clicks that last piece loses.

fields.text: Are you sure you want to restart the game?
